You channel [[primal magic]] to cause your teeth or fingernails to sharpen and imbue with acidic energy, ready to deliver a corrosive attack. Attacking a nearby enemy with your natural weapons deals extra [[acid damage|damage type]]. After you make the attack, your teeth or fingernails return to normal.